name: The Beak of the Bird
description: @ArtPunkLars | The Belly is Full, the Beak is Empty. Beak is scratched, worn and dirty. the belly is full of nutrients and ulcers. The Beak is connected to the backbone. The Belly is connected to the arsehole. Co-dependency. A parasite calls The Belly its residency. will the Beak ever be set free?
